# Creating a Secure IPsec Site to Site Tunnel between two sites 

## Overview
This project connects Site A and Site B via a VPN 
using IKE PHase and and IKE Phase 2 


## Features
- Three Routers, 1 for ISP , 1 for Site A and another for Site B 
- Each site has a Layer 2 switch and there are two Pcs under each
- Proper cable types and interface configuration
- Connectivity testing with ping 

## Files in this Repository
- PacketTracer/Creating a secure Site to Site VPN tunnel between two sites .pkt 
- Documentation.docx â€” project documentation

## How to Use
1. Download `.pkt` file
2. Open in Cisco Packet Tracer
3. Test connectivity and verify the VPN tunnel is working accordingly by running "sh crypto ipsec sa"
on the Site A and Site B Router 
